name: ormsgpack

about.summary: Fast, correct Python msgpack library supporting dataclasses, datetimes, and numpy

raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: ormsgpack
  version: "1.12.2"

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/ormsgpack-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 944a2233640273bee67521795a73cf1e959538e0dfb7ac635505010455e53b33

build:
  number: 0
  script:
    - cargo-bundle-licenses --format yaml --output THIRDPARTY.yml
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  build:
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('rust') }}
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
  host:
    - python
    - maturin >=1.0,<2.0
    - pip
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - ormsgpack
      pip_check: true

about:
  summary: Fast, correct Python msgpack library supporting dataclasses, datetimes, and numpy
  license: MIT AND Apache-2.0
  license_file:
    - LICENSE-APACHE
    - LICENSE-MIT
    - THIRDPARTY.yml
  homepage: https://github.com/aviramha/ormsgpack

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
